{"lemma":"ثاقِبُو","slug":"ثاقِبُو","root":"ث.ق.ب","root_slug":"ث-ق-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-ق-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ثاقِب","root":"ثقب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4531"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"penetrating"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of ثَقَبَ (ṯaqaba)."},"ipa":["/θaː.qib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4531","headword_ar":"ثَاقِبٌ","root":"vqb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  A star, and a lamp, and fire, (A,) or a flame of fire, or a shooting star, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shining brightly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shining, glistening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleaming, very brightly, as though piercing through the darkness, and dispelling it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ajomu Alv~aAqibu","text_ar":"النَّجْمُ الثَّاقِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the Kur lxxxvi. 3] means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism, brightly shining;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Bd, L;) as though it pierced through the darkness, or the celestial spheres, by its light: (Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the star,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism, that is high, above the others:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the planet Saturn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Pleiades,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any star"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism, brightly shining;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it pierces through the darkness by its light. (Jel.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)  A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zanod","text_ar":"زَنْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that emits fire, when struck."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  Applied to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasab","text_ar":"حَسَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. nobility, or grounds of pretension to respect or honour], it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Famous and exalted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, JK, A, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bright; brilliant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA.) ―         -b4-  And hence, (tropical:)  applied to knowledge [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Penetrating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brilliant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (As, TA.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaAqibu AlEilomi","text_ar":"ثَاقِبُ العِلْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaAqibN","text_ar":"ثَاقِبٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlEilomi","text_ar":"فِى العِلْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Brilliant"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"penetrating"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in knowledge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivoqabN","text_ar":"مِثْقَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) which latter signifies also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"learned, and sagacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intelligent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"penetrating in judgment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaAqibu Alr~aA^oYi","text_ar":"ثَاقِبُ الرَّاْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sound and penetrating judgment, sagacity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intelligence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atatoniY Eanohumo EayonN vaAqibapN","text_ar":"اَتَتْنِى عَنْهُمْ عَيْنٌ ثَاقِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanoka","text_ar":"عَنْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There came to me, from them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from thee, certain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sure, news"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"information."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, A, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN vaAqibN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ ثَاقِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel having much milk; abounding with milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, JK, S, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaqiybN","text_ar":"ثَقِيبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AZ, JK, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaqiybapN","text_ar":"ثَقِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqiybapN","text_ar":"نَقِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl. (of the former, A)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwqN vuqubN","text_ar":"نُوقٌ ثُقُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in a copy of the A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vuq~abN","text_ar":"ثُقَّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlA_ibili","text_ar":"مِنَ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahaA lavaqiybN","text_ar":"اـِنَّهَا لَثَقِيبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily she is one that vies with the other camels abounding with milk, and surpasses them in abundance thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","S","Bd","L","K","TA","JK"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}